               <msContents>
                  <summary>F<locus target="#1r">fols. 1r, </locus>-xxx: Mystagogia, ትምህርተ፡ ኅቡዓት፡. HTexte 48–72; Textes 40–52; Me‘erāf I 215–7; MG 9ff.  F<locus target="#14r">14r, </locus>-29r: Image of Michael, Mälk‘a Mika’el, መልክአ፡ ሚካኤል፡. Répertoire 119. Incipit : ሰላም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምከ፡ ምስለ: ስመ: ልዑል: ዘተሳተፈ:. MG 290ff. EMIP 16, <locus target="#92v">92v, </locus>; EMIP 56, <locus target="#1r">1r, </locus>; MYS 6, f<locus target="#39r">39r, </locus>–66v, 2066/Tweed 117, 2071/Tweed 122. F<locus target="#14r">14r, </locus> and 19r and 46v mention an owner ወልደ ጸድቅ. F<locus target="#19r">19r, </locus>-46v: Image of Saint George zä-Säläda Mogäs, መልክአ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ዘሰሌዳ፡ ሞገስ።  incipit: ሰላም: ለዝክረ: ስምከ: ዘሰሌዳ: ሞገስ: መጽሐፉ:  Répertoire 147. F<locus target="#48r">48r, </locus>-53r: Angels Praise Her, Yǝwedǝssǝwa Mäla’ǝkt, ይዌድስዋ፡ መላእክት፡ ለማርያም፡. Répertoire 388; MD 519ff. ; EMML 1593, <locus target="#92a">92a, </locus>. F<locus target="#46r">46r, </locus>-61v: Hymn to Mary, commonly called “Image of Edom,” መልክዐ፡ ኤዶም፡. Répertoire 221; MG 651ff. F<locus target="#61v">61v, </locus>-71v: Image of Gabriel, Mälk‘a Gäbra’el, መልክአ፡ ገብርኤል፡, incipit: ሰላመ: ገብርኤል: መልአክ: በላዕለ: ማርያም: ዘአዕረፈ:. Répertoire 246; MG 312ff. F<locus target="#73r">73r, </locus>-95r: Image of Jesus Christ, Mälk‘a Iyyäsus, መልክአ፡  ኢየሱስ፡. Répertoire 123. Incipit : ሰላም ለዝክረ ሰምኪ ስመ መሐላ ዘኢየኄሱ. Varia: F<locus target="#46v">46v, </locus>-47r: Magic Prayer based on Dersana Mika'el.  <locus target="#95v">95v</locus>: excerpt from Image of Jesus Christ, in another untrained hand. </summary>
